dct_title_s: Description du pais Normandie; par Damien de Templeux Escuyer Sr. du Frestoy.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes ill. of ships and sea creatures, and uses a special engraving technique to create a wave appearance in the water. The scall cartouche includes the date "1620." From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 32 x 51 cm.
dct_creator_sm: Templeux, Damien de, Sieur de Frestoy, engraver
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
